Package org.eclipse.dataset.function

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatasetToDatasetFunction
    This interface is to define functions that take datasets and returns a list of datasets
    DatasetToNumberFunction
    This interface is to define functions that take a dataset or an array of datasets and returns numbers (which could be complex and so returned as pairs)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Centroid
    Find centroid of each dataset and return list of centroids along each dataset's axes
    LineSample
    Sample along line and return list of one 1D dataset When mapping from image to data, the array value is assumed to be associated with the centre of the pixel, i.e.
    MapToRotatedCartesian
    Map a 2D dataset from Cartesian to rotated Cartesian coordinates and return that remapped dataset from a rotated rectangle return a dataset and an unclipped unit version (for clipping compensation)
